01:14:06.037 --> 01:14:08.205
among other things.

01:14:08.239 --> 01:14:10.574
Look,

01:14:10.609 --> 01:14:12.543
just tell me
you got something.

01:14:15.047 --> 01:14:18.417
No.
No, we're nowhere.

01:14:18.451 --> 01:14:20.018
