for Morgan Stanley?

01:14:20.052 --> 01:14:24.055
China Investment
Corporation.

01:14:25.224 --> 01:14:27.491
Mae Mitsubishi.

01:14:27.525 --> 01:14:30.128
No, the Japanese will
never do this deal.

01:14:30.162 --> 01:14:31.730
How about Goldman?

01:14:31.764 --> 01:14:34.633
Goldman's looking at Wachovia,
but they're so fucked,

01:14:34.667 --> 01:14:36.668
